%% SmartGrid DW v2 — non-breaking migration (current path stays live throughout)
flowchart TB
    classDef additive fill:#D3F9D8,stroke:#2F9E44,color:#0B3D1B;
    classDef cut fill:#FFE3E3,stroke:#E03131,color:#5C0000;
    classDef neutral fill:#F1F3F5,stroke:#868E96,color:#212529;

    P0["Phase 0<br/>Guardrails<br/>tag + snapshot"]:::neutral
    P1["Phase 1<br/>Create dimensions (dw)<br/>seed from public.*"]:::additive
    P2["Phase 2<br/>Build + backfill facts<br/>validate parity"]:::additive
    P3["Phase 3<br/>Dual-write<br/>old path stays primary"]:::additive
    P4["Phase 4<br/>Repoint reads to dw.v_*<br/>Grafana + ML validate"]:::additive
    P5["Phase 5<br/>Cutover: legacy names<br/>become compat views"]:::cut
    P6["Phase 6<br/>Decommission<br/>drop _legacy (optional)"]:::neutral

    P0 --> P1 --> P2 --> P3 --> P4 --> P5 --> P6

    subgraph LIVE[Current system keeps working]
        L1["public.meter_readings / meter_predictions / anomaly_events<br/>+ Grafana + ML unchanged through Phases 1-4;<br/>preserved as views from Phase 5"]:::neutral
    end

    P1 -. additive .-> LIVE
    P4 -. validated .-> LIVE
    P5 == views ==> LIVE
